<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle;"><b>Signature</b><br />
<a href="/wiki/File:Albert_Einstein_signature.svg" class="image" title="Albert Einstein's signature"><img alt="Albert Einstein's signature" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/44/Albert_Einstein_signature.svg/128px-Albert_Einstein_signature.svg.png" width="128" height="32" border="0" /></a></td>
