<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFEinstein1901">Einstein, Albert (1901), "Folgerungen aus den Capillaritätserscheinungen (Conclusions Drawn from the Phenomena of Capillarity)", <i>Annalen der Physik</i> <b>4</b>: 513, <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2Fandp.19013090306" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1002%2Fandp.19013090306" rel="nofollow">10.1002/andp.19013090306</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Folgerungen+aus+den+Capillarit%C3%A4tserscheinungen+%28Conclusions+Drawn+from+the+Phenomena+of+Capillarity%29&amp;rft.jtitle=Annalen+der+Physik&amp;rft.aulast=Einstein&amp;rft.aufirst=Albert&amp;rft.au=Einstein%2C+Albert&amp;rft.date=1901&amp;rft.volume=4&amp;rft.pages=513&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1002%2Fandp.19013090306&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Albert_Einstein"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
