<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFEinstein1905b">Einstein, Albert (1905b), <i>A new determination of molecular dimensions</i></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+new+determination+of+molecular+dimensions&amp;rft.aulast=Einstein&amp;rft.aufirst=Albert&amp;rft.au=Einstein%2C+Albert&amp;rft.date=1905b&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Albert_Einstein"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>. This PhD thesis was completed 30 April and submitted 20 July.</li>
