<li><a href="http://www.dmoz.org/Science/Physics/History/People/Einstein,_Albert/" class="external text" title="http://www.dmoz.org/Science/Physics/History/People/Einstein,_Albert/" rel="nofollow">Albert Einstein</a> at the <a href="/wiki/Open_Directory_Project" title="Open Directory Project">Open Directory Project</a></li>
